                        <note rend="inline" type="source">500.A4e/561: Telegram</note>
                        <head><hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to
                                the <gloss type="to">American Delegation</gloss></hi></head>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1926-03-03T17:00:00-05:00"><hi rend="italic">March 3,
                                        1926—5 p.m.</hi></date></dateline></opener>
                        <p>12. Your Conference 26, March 3, 3 p.m. Your attitude regarding
                            negotiations approved.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Kellogg</hi></signed></closer>
